snippet.title: Amber Heard Holds Hands With New Girlfriend And Has A Very Touching Moment With A Deaf Fan
snippet.description:
Amber Heard looks smitten at the Los Angeles Women's March as she's spotted holding hands with girlfriend and cinematographer, Bianca Butti. The Aquaman actress also has a very touching encounter with a deaf fan as the duo exchange pleasantries through sign language.
